Package jakarta.ws.rs

Annotation Type GET

@Target(METHOD)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@HttpMethod("GET")
@Documented
public @interface GET
Indicates that the annotated method responds to HTTP GET requests.

1.0
Author:
